title: REMOVED: La Tolderia
typeOfFood: Lacto, Pizza, Italian, Western, Beer/Wine, Argentinian , Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Standard restaurant by day, then a club & bar by night from 1am on. Has vegetarian dishes but not much for vegans except salads. Reported staff will try to accommodate when you ask to omit cheese/dairy, but you have to be very specific. Not much else for veg food in this region.
